			<wp:comment_content><![CDATA[So, this is an early version of targeting ads, contextualizing ads, ala google ads?  Cool.

Gotta tell you that I was always intrigued by and attracted to the ads in the back of comics too.  It always seemed impossible to get the things those ads promised: magic sea horses (or whatever they were), x-ray glasses, etc.  All the stuff that a comic book reading kid would want, to become a super hero, perhaps - or simply to become the envy of the neighbourhood.  For me, those were only ever wish items.

Am I revealing too many personal insecurities?

-Tad]]></wp:comment_content>
