		<title>#120 Comics &#038; The Multimodal World - An International Conference</title>
		<link>http://www.graphixia.ca/2013/06/comics-the-multimodal-world-an-international-conference/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2013 14:31:05 +0000</pubDate>
