			<wp:comment_date_gmt>2014-07-07 23:12:52</wp:comment_date_gmt>
			<wp:comment_content><![CDATA[Thank you for analysis.  When Lemire introduced the country nurse it shows a good glimpse into how he viewed this town. Anne meddles, and where she does so she quite literally attempts to heal more than just the physical wounds of these guys.  Sure, she could be viewed as a plot device, but we see plenty of her self-doubt in regards to her role, and also her longing for more with her own family.

