		<title>#210 Speed Machines in Early Comic Strips</title>
		<link>http://www.graphixia.ca/2015/07/210-speed-machines-in-early-comic-strips/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2015 23:11:22 +0000</pubDate>
