<i>(b) </i>Ro, R. (2004) <i>Tales to astonish: Jack Kirby, Stan Lee, and the American comic book revolution</i>, New York: Bloomsbury, p.99

<i>(c) </i>Howe, S. (2012) <i>Marvel comics: the untold story</i>, New York: Harper, pp.194-195

<i>(d) </i>Evanier, M. (2008) <i>Kirby: king of comics</i>, Abrams, New York, p.187

