		<title>#250 Bakuman, Translations, Authenticity, and Otherness</title>
		<link>http://www.graphixia.ca/2016/09/250-bakuman-translations-authenticity-and-otherness/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 Sep 2016 03:35:30 +0000</pubDate>
